Blight: "You would not be able to comprhend the designs do to your lack of 
intelligence. Besides you would probably mess them up. I really don't know 
why we are dealing with such incompetent beings as you robots. but that can't 
be helped. And we need more then shuttles and drones, we requested half of 
your men. Not drones. Another example of your races incopetence."

Blight facepalms as he shakes his head, laughing to himself as he does.
